# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and working tree.
# This project is developed/tested/deployed on Linux (CI, Docker, air-gap) and
# every file was committed with LF. Editors on Windows must not reintroduce
# CRLF: doing so flips every line and shows hundreds of phantom "changes".
# git now enforces LF on add and checkout regardless of host OS.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binaries — never line-ending normalized.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.zip  binary
*.gz   binary
*.whl  binary
*.db   binary
*.xlsx binary
*.docx binary
*.pptx binary
